@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam roundCorner 15
skinparam ArrowColor #555555
[*] --> Pending
Pending --> Created : reject
Pending : entry / log route
Created --> Draft : cancel
Draft --> Archived : confirm
Archived --> Closed : approve
Closed --> Delivered : process
Archived --> Closed : revert
Delivered --> [*]
@enduml